{"tid":1120782,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"黑色劇透警告即將生效","createTime":"2019-04-23T02:01:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-23T09:07:29.000Z","uid":64191,"like":34,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e5dfb870b450cb45bec9d38f56b20193db2f26b9","tid":1120782,"uid":64191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T02:01:43.000Z","msg":"首先，大陸於今晚凌晨12點播放首場《復仇者聯盟4》，預料凌晨三點開始，世界各大網絡將會充斥支那人劇透既消息。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港亦隨之播放首場，預計早上7-10時左右會有第一輪劇透。在此向害怕劇透既朋友呼籲，請於今晚12點後全速撤離，避免翻閱任何電影、娛樂新聞、社交媒體、農場文網站，以免影響觀賞既驚喜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然，唔怕劇透，純粹享受聲畫娛樂既，就可以無視呢項警告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10bd96e9f031c2ec049b26248405108abda19ea3","tid":1120782,"uid":162316,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T02:20:24.000Z","msg":"唔好講支那人啦<br />\n連登都大把on9仔玩title劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"822ce08935a6f9e59b0cc058c904577578ff1db5","tid":1120782,"uid":238673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T02:26:54.000Z","msg":"無視mode<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c2dda7616775aeb553c1451e457fec037475b5","tid":1120782,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T02:30:50.000Z","msg":"唔好on9<br />\n2個鐘之後已經會有劇透<br />\nLA首映緊<br />\n岩岩開始左1個鐘左右<br />\n大家好走喇"},{"pid":"1753385a1e67497b924e6b909c859b6c1045bf5a","tid":1120782,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-23T03:01:15.000Z","msg":"之前已經有人貼左編中國劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n忍左手無睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e6edbceba2148cf4a90b90dfb83a38cea00875","tid":1120782,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17